    "The five bins for abnormal are presented as 22.712 (95% CI: 21.050 to 24.323), 28.470 (95% CI: 27.411 to 29.528), 33.359 (95% CI: 32.298 to 34.497), 41.729 (95% CI: 40.406 to 43.045) and 43.904 (95% CI: 39.488 to 48.428)."
